1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,937
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:24,559 --> 00:00:25,440
You've come.

4
00:00:26,399 --> 00:00:27,079
You two

5
00:00:28,039 --> 00:00:29,000
know each other?

6
00:00:29,879 --> 00:00:30,800
Little girl,

7
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,359
you didn't truly think

8
00:00:34,079 --> 00:00:35,920
I would actually wager against you?

9
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:37,880
I lured you here

10
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,799
to hand you over to Commissioner Luo.

11
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,359
The condition was

12
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:43,840
that he would destroy all of my records.

13
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,439
Every single one of them.

14
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:47,560
That way, I can finally

15
00:00:47,759 --> 00:00:50,560
live as an ordinary man
with my head held high.

16
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:54,679
It seems you've been in league
with the Gate Bureau all along.

17
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:57,840
Those who understand the times

18
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,520
can live a long life.

19
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,040
You've lost.

20
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:08,079
Commissioner Luo,
you truly have superb chess skills.

21
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:15,359
So you are the Sect Leader of
the Sacred Hand Sect, the Jade Squirrel.

22
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:17,480
Correct.

23
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,680
Surrender now.

24
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,400
I can spare your life.

25
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,079
That depends on your own ability.

26
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,760
Where is the Sacred Token?

27
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,920
Isn't it with you?

28
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:43,519
It isn't with me.

29
00:01:53,437 --> 00:01:56,135
(Boundless Loyalty)

30
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,120
Commissioner Luo,

31
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:59,560
why aren't you pursuing her?

32
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,640
Don't just stand there!

33
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,760
Don't think...

34
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,040
(Boundless Loyalty)
Do you know who you are talking to?

35
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,120
You...

36
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,280
Stop putting on airs.

37
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,360
Others might not know your history,

38
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,560
but do you think I don't?

39
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:16,275
(Boundless Loyalty)

40
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,680
Chu Yunchang.

41
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,199
Hand over the Sacred Token.

42
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,960
Go ask him for it!

43
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:47,120
You just killed him to silence him,

44
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,439
and now you're pinning it on a dead man?

45
00:02:49,687 --> 00:02:51,879
Do you really think
I'm that easy to deal with?

46
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:52,919
Grandfather!

47
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,599
Wushuang?

48
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,560
Jade Squirrel, I'll kill you!

49
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,180
Stop right there!

50
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,719
Stop!

51
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:24,960
Hurry!

52
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:25,719
Let's go!

53
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,399
I have confirmed

54
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,519
that Chu Yunchang is the Jade Squirrel.

55
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,360
What if

56
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,199
I were the Jade Squirrel?

57
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,399
What would you do?

58
00:04:27,575 --> 00:04:30,787
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

59
00:04:31,262 --> 00:04:34,875
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

60
00:04:34,962 --> 00:04:39,200
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

61
00:04:39,325 --> 00:04:42,950
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

62
00:04:43,412 --> 00:04:46,825
♪I long for it so much,
I crave to return♪

63
00:04:47,062 --> 00:04:50,550
♪To the moment we first met♪

64
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,199
Master?

65
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,480
Master?

66
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,160
Are you back, Master?

67
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:58,720
I heard the Jade Squirrel
and Dongfang Qing caused quite a scene

68
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,839
at the Gate Bureau.

69
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,439
Dongfang Qing is dead.

70
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,160
Did you see the Jade Squirrel?

71
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,800
I didn't.

72
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:09,160
Weren't you on vacation in Tangshan?

73
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,839
Why are you back so suddenly?

74
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:12,279
I came to get something.

75
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,600
I see.

76
00:05:31,012 --> 00:05:31,692
(Medicine chest?)

77
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,639
(Who delivered this?)

78
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,399
(Could it be Wuxia?)

79
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,790
(The wound was caused
by the Commissioner's hidden weapon.)

80
00:06:16,730 --> 00:06:19,759
(There is a vast difference in strength
between him and the Jade Squirrel.)

81
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,600
(Why did the Commissioner...)

82
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,240
Yu?

83
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,720
Yu, I know you're in there.

84
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,600
Yu, open the door.

85
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,560
Yu!

86
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,319
Wushuang.

87
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,639
What brings you here?

88
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:51,600
Buyu.

89
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,399
Where were you going in that outfit?

90
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:58,000
Weren't you at the Tangshan hot spring?

91
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,399
Why are you here?

92
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,240
I forgot an important official document.

93
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,040
Don't try to fool me.

94
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:06,519
I saw you rescue the Jade Squirrel
with my own eyes.

95
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,260
With your own eyes?

96
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,560
Are you sure it was me you saw?

97
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:10,959
Stop trying to brush me off.

98
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,399
I know she's in there.

99
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,560
Yu, at this point,

100
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:16,480
you must stop lying to yourself.

101
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,079
Take my advice.

102
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,439
Hand over Chu Yunchang.

103
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,399
The great credit
for capturing the Jade Squirrel

104
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:23,079
can be all yours.

105
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:26,759
Do not jump to conclusions
without evidence.

106
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:27,759
Evidence?

107
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,439
Chu Yunchang and Dongfang Qing
fought each other,

108
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,920
and she killed him to silence him.

109
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,720
Dongfang Qing's body

110
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,199
is in my grandfather's room now.

111
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,040
Chu Yunchang was wounded
by my grandfather.

112
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,040
She's in your room now, right?

113
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,279
If you don't believe me,

114
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,839
remove her mask and see for yourself.

115
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,639
If you won't do it, I will.

116
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,439
Sister?

117
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,120
What are you doing here?

118
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:02,000
I'm helping Master find some documents.

119
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:07,319
Are you the only one in this room?

120
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,519
Yes.

121
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,930
I don't believe it.

122
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,199
Sister!

123
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,559
Where is she?

124
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:38,679
Who?

125
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:41,799
I told you, it's just the two of us.

126
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,679
I don't believe a word of it, Luo Wuxia.

127
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,960
You'd better tell me the truth.

128
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,200
Sister.

129
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:49,279
I know you like Master,

130
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,159
but barging into his room

131
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,799
in the middle of the night

132
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,559
is inappropriate.

133
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,440
Shut up, unless you want a beating.

134
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,759
Master.

135
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,919
You really owe me one this time.

136
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,919
You'll have to repay the favor.

137
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,679
Do you know what you are doing?

138
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,519
I don't.

139
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,679
However,

140
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:38,159
as long as you know what you're doing,
that's enough.

141
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:52,320
Get them!

142
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:53,399
Dead or alive!

143
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:53,960
- Yes!
- Yes!

144
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,120
Master.

145
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,720
Who was that person
in your room just now?

146
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,559
You already know, don't you?

147
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,840
Why even ask me?

148
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:05,200
It really was the Jade Squirrel!

149
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:08,720
I actually saved the Jade Squirrel!

150
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:11,200
All that hard work at the Gate Bureau

151
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,399
was all worth it.

152
00:10:13,162 --> 00:10:14,442
She's my idol!

153
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,720
You're a man of the law.

154
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,480
Don't you think she's guilty?

155
00:10:20,710 --> 00:10:21,799
It doesn't really matter.

156
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,240
That's the higher-ups' concern.

157
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:27,240
What I mean is,

158
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,320
our job at the Gate Bureau
is just to make the arrests.

159
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:33,360
Besides, even while
I was away from the Capital,

160
00:10:33,430 --> 00:10:35,919
I'd heard about the good deeds
of the Sacred Hand Sect Leader.

161
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,600
The common folk have
nothing but praise for her.

162
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,370
Why does someone like that

163
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:43,080
have to die?

164
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,480
Impressive.

165
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:50,120
You're starting to sound
more like a constable every day.

166
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,519
Naturally.

167
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:11,919
Chang?

168
00:11:14,475 --> 00:11:15,075
Chang?

169
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,440
Chang?

170
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,679
I'm so sorry!

171
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,440
My apologies.

172
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,480
Get out!

173
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,480
(How reckless of me.)

174
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:12,440
Chang.

175
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:14,879
I wanted to see
if you were feeling better.

176
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,159
I'm fine. I'm going to sleep now.

177
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,000
You should get some rest too.

178
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,320
He's gone.

179
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:44,159
Chang!

180
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:47,759
Chang!

181
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,120
Chang!

182
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,000
Stop it, pervert!

183
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,200
Stop!

184
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,200
Goodness! Are you all right?

185
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:03,960
Yunchang!

186
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,759
Stop right there, scoundrel!

187
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,399
Little Sister, aren't you
overdoing it a bit?

188
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,240
I'm not your sister.

189
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,080
It's me.

190
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:29,200
I'm your brother.

191
00:13:29,675 --> 00:13:31,700
(Chu Yunchang's father, Chu Xiangshan)

192
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,919
It's been seven years.

193
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,600
Where have you been?

194
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,000
Seven years ago,

195
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,639
you vanished without a word.

196
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,559
You just left everything to me.

197
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,200
I was but a woman.

198
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:58,519
Not only did I
have to raise Chang alone,

199
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,960
but I had to
keep this entire family afloat.

200
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,240
And now you think you can just

201
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,759
waltz back whenever you please?

202
00:14:09,039 --> 00:14:10,559
What kind of brother are you?

203
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,840
I'm sorry.

204
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,360
I failed you.

205
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,080
Listen closely.

206
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:24,120
I have taken excellent care of Chang.

207
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:27,480
She doesn't have a father anymore.

208
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,840
We don't need you.

209
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:29,639
Just leave!

210
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:30,320
Xiangling...

211
00:14:38,679 --> 00:14:39,679
This is all my fault.

212
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:46,960
My dear.

213
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:50,720
I'm sure your brother has
his reasons for staying away.

214
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:52,799
Don't be so hard on him.

215
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:10,879
Chang.

216
00:15:11,759 --> 00:15:12,320
Chang!

217
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,080
Chang!

218
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,639
It's me.

219
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,559
I'm back.

220
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:29,480
I must be dreaming.

221
00:15:29,799 --> 00:15:30,480
Chang.

222
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:31,759
Don't be afraid.

223
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,480
Your father really is back.

224
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,080
Chang.

225
00:15:37,759 --> 00:15:38,679
I'm home.

226
00:15:45,799 --> 00:15:47,320
Where have you been all these years?

227
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,639
Why come back now?

228
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,519
It's a long story.

229
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,000
Chang,

230
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,200
please believe me.

231
00:15:57,879 --> 00:16:01,080
Everything I did was to protect you

232
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:02,559
and this family.

233
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,639
Fine words.

234
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:06,559
You vanished for seven long years.

235
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,240
To protect this family?

236
00:16:08,639 --> 00:16:10,000
What have you ever done for us?

237
00:16:10,679 --> 00:16:11,759
That's enough.

238
00:16:13,799 --> 00:16:14,480
Sister.

239
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,759
Chang.

240
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:20,240
I still can't tell you exactly

241
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,200
where I've been all this time.

242
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,559
But you must believe me,

243
00:16:25,759 --> 00:16:26,720
throughout these years,

244
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,320
not once did I stop searching

245
00:16:29,759 --> 00:16:31,559
for our sect's greatest treasure.

246
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:33,960
The Sacred Token.

247
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,120
Well? Did you find it?

248
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,480
Chang?

249
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,320
Are you feeling better?

250
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,240
May I come in?

251
00:16:52,587 --> 00:16:55,862
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

252
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:58,775
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

253
00:16:59,275 --> 00:17:04,993
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

254
00:17:06,175 --> 00:17:09,495
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

255
00:17:09,625 --> 00:17:12,545
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

256
00:17:13,713 --> 00:17:18,953
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

257
00:17:20,175 --> 00:17:22,568
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

258
00:17:22,568 --> 00:17:26,218
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

259
00:17:26,287 --> 00:17:29,777
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

260
00:17:29,875 --> 00:17:32,850
♪To the ends of time♪

261
00:17:32,850 --> 00:17:36,225
♪The moon traces your face♪

262
00:17:36,412 --> 00:17:40,000
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

263
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:46,240
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

264
00:17:46,575 --> 00:17:49,790
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

265
00:17:50,075 --> 00:17:53,613
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

266
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,925
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

267
00:17:56,925 --> 00:18:00,025
♪On our way to forever♪

268
00:18:00,025 --> 00:18:03,875
♪The moon traces your face♪

269
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:07,235
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

270
00:18:07,425 --> 00:18:13,385
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

271
00:18:14,462 --> 00:18:24,102
♪Just to be with you♪
